added.all_hanging_signs: • Used in the #all_signs block tag.
added.combination_step_sound_blocks: • Controls which blocks can produce a combination of step sounds.
added.enchantment_power_transmitter: • Contains blocks that do not invalidate enchanting bonuses when placed between a enchanting table and bookshelves.
added.maintains_farmland: • Contains blocks that will not cause farmland to be converted into dirt when placed on top of it.
added.replaceable:
• Contains blocks on which another block can be placed.
  • Used in the #enchantment_power_transmitter block tag.
added.replaceable_by_trees: • Contains changeable blocks that growing trees can replace.
added.sword_efficient: • Contains blocks that break faster with a sword.
